* {{flagicon|Ontario}} '''1985''': [[University of Toronto]], Doctor of Laws (LLD)
* {{flagicon|Quebec}} '''1986''': [[Bishop's University]], Doctor of Laws (LLD)
* {{flagicon|Newfoundland and Labrador}} '''1986''': [[Memorial University of Newfoundland]], Doctor of Laws (LLD)
* {{flagicon|Quebec}} '''1987''': [[Montreal Diocesan Theological College]], [[Doctor of Divinity]] (DD)
* {{flagicon|British Columbia}} '''1989''': [[University of British Columbia]], Doctor of Laws (LLD)
* {{flagicon|Ontario}} '''1991''': [[Queen's University]], Doctor of Laws (LLD)
* {{flagicon|Ontario}} '''1991''': [[University of Western Ontario]], Doctor of Laws (LLD)
* {{flagicon|Quebec}} '''1992''': [[Universit<U+00E9> de Montr<U+00E9>al]], Doctor of Laws (LLD)
* {{flagicon|Ontario}} '''1993''': [[Algoma University]], Doctor of Laws (LLD)
* {{flagicon|British Columbia}} '''1994''': [[University of Victoria]], Doctor of Laws (LLD)
* {{flagicon|Quebec}} '''2000''': [[McGill University]], Doctor of Laws (LLD)
* {{flagicon|Ontario}} '''2008''': [[McMaster University]], Doctor of Laws (LLD)<ref name=CV6 /><ref name=cbcbio />

